{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope.origin","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/origin","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/origin\"><code>Origin</code></a></strong></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope</code></a> インターフェイスの読み取り専用プロパティ&nbsp;<code><strong>origin</strong></code>&nbsp;は、グローバルスコープの文字列としてシリアライズされた&nbsp;origin を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>myOrigin</em> = self.origin; // or just origin\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"値","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>worker script 内から実行される以下のスニペットは、メッセージを受け取る度にワーカーのグローバルスコープの origin をコンソールに記録します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onmessage</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>origin<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>もし origin が scheme/host/port tuple出ない場合 (あなたがローカルで実行しようとしている、言い換えると&nbsp;<code>file://</code>&nbsp;というURLの場合)、&nbsp;<code>origin</code>&nbsp;は&nbsp;<code>\"null\"</code>&nbsp;という文字列を返すでしょう。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">ステータス</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#dom-origin\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope.origin の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザ互換性","id":"ブラウザ互換性","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope.origin","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"},{"text":"ブラウザ互換性","id":"ブラウザ互換性"}],"summary":"WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope インターフェイスの読み取り専用プロパティ origin は、グローバルスコープの文字列としてシリアライズされた origin を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"origin","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"origin","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"origin","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/origin","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/origin/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":